The paper focuses on understanding the dynamic structure of video ads and predicting sentiment, which involves analyzing both visual and audio cues as well as context features. This suggests that the paper could fall under multiple sub-categories, including multimedia (cs.MM), information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG).
